<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>ḥy hw ạlrb ạ̹lhy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ḥyuⁿ hw ạlrb ạ̹lhy .. ạlly ạ̉nạ wạqf qdạmh
 ḥyuⁿ sydy ạlmlk ạlly .. ạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ kẖdạmh)2
 1- (lạ ạ̉nạ kẖạyf mn sẖyʾ ạ̹n kạn .. wlạ mn mkẖlwq mhmạ ạ̹n kạn)2
 wlạ mḥtạj sẖyʾ mn ạ̹nsạn .. dh mkfyny slạmh
 2- (ạ̉nạ ʿạkf ʿly̱ ạlmktwb .. ḍd ạlṭyạr ạlmqlwb)2
 ạ̉sẖhd lyswʿ ạlmḥbwb .. wạtsẖạrk fy ậlạmh
 3- (ạ̉nạ sẖạyf ậkẖr ạlmsẖwạr .. jạy ạlfjr wjạy nhạr)2
 wlḥd ạlsẖr mạ ynhạr .. ạ̉nạ hạrfʿ ạ̉ʿlạmh
 4- (ạ̉nạ ʿạrf ạ̹ymạny bmyn .. ạlqạdr yḥfẓny ạ̉myn)2
 jạy whạsẖwfh bkl yqyn .. zy mạ wʿd fy klạmh
 5- (ạ̉nạ wạqf mstny wʿwd .. ttḥqq wạlmjd yʿwd)2
 wnqf kdh ṣfyn bạlʿwd .. wnʿly fy ạ̉ngẖạmh</lyrics>
</song>